snippet.title: Shawn Wasabi - Marble Soda (Live Mashup)
snippet.description:
a live mashup of a bunch of my favorite songs and sounds :)

http://shawnwasabi.com
http://soundcloud.com/sssshawnnnn
http://twitter.com/shawnwasabi
http://instagram.com/shawnwasabi

performed on a Midi Fighter 64 
custom built by Michael Mitchell - (THANK YOU MIKE)

~more info~
controller: Midi Fighter 64 Shawn Wasabi Special Edition
program: Ableton Live 9
button on the bottom left triggers banks
4 buttons on the bottom right trigger banks within banks
everything else is sounds
